name: The monoliths #4
description: The fourth piece in the monoliths series was sent to @mikefagundes on the 18th of September 2021 in the second year of the pandemic. It was not a bad day if a little warm and a little humid. This is the second piece in a row for @mikefagundes and a good place to say *thank you* and note that a third alternate piece for the series will at some point find its way to your wallet.
